{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_12071.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":800100,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narration":"(Narration by Reginald Kingston III)","narrationBg":"black","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"bgm":"bgm03_movie12","nameNarration":"???","narration":"Natural-born beauty is not something@that can be obtained, regardless of@how hard you might yearn for it.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_12071.jpg"},{"narration":"This may be the prime reason that beauty@is placed on such a high pedestal."},{"chara":[{"id":800100}],"nameCenter":"","narrationEffect":"out","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"Aaaaaaah! Riaaaaaa!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":800200,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narration":"This girl, however, possesses such@overwhelming beauty that wherever she@goes, the crowds part to let her pass.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_12071.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"id":800200,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameCenter":"","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"She's more gorgeous than ever..."},{"narration":"Voices from every direction can@be heard raving about her looks.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_12071.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narration":"This is Ria Ami.","narrationBg":""},{"narration":"You are incredibly popular."},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"nameCenter":"Ria","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Oh, it's been this way since I was young."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"So for me this is normal."},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textCenter":"To be honest, I have no sense of my own@popularity at all."},{"narration":"Is it hard to be watched every day?","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"It has its challenges, yes."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"Sometimes I even feel it is quite difficult."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":1}],"textCenter":"But it's also good in a way."},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textCenter":"When people pay so much attention to me..."},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"motion":0}],"textCenter":"I become more conscious of my posture."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"It inspires me to be more beautiful, and I@don't just mean in terms of appearance."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"More like, as a human being?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001}],"textCenter":"I think it helps me be more beautiful as a @person."},{"narration":"Even her words, so full of humility, are@imbued with that classic Ria Ami grace.","narrationEffect":"in"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":301001,"motion":0}],"narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Well, I'm afraid I must go to school now,@so do pardon me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"Oh my goooshhh! Riaaaaaa!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301001,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Ria","textLeft":"Nice to see you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":800300,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameRight":"","textBg":"shout","textRight":"Aaahhhhhh! She noticed us!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":300901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Manaka","textRight":"Senpai! Ria-senpai!"},{"chara":[{"id":301001}],"textLeft":"Good day."},{"chara":[{"id":300901}],"textRight":"Um, your face."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"textLeft":"[chara:301001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"id":301001,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"(My face? What?! Is there something on@my face?!)"},{"nameNarration":"Ria","narration":"Yes, that's right.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnEffect":"stop"},{"narration":"Something happened in my past@that I can never tell anyone."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}